  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I found out the very first day that, unfortunately, they do not need a Yiddish teacher in Atlanta, they need a Hebrew teacher.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So, sort of, I was stuck in Atlanta.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But I am happy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I was happy, and I am happy that [INAUDIBLE] Atlanta.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I had different jobs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I held different jobs, very hard.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I had a very hard beginning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The first 10 years, very hard.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Very often, I was thinking if I did the right thing to come to the United States.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But this was temporary.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I have to say-- I have to say that some survivors who are living in Atlanta helped us a lot.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I don't know if I should mention names, names of the people who helped us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Borenstein, ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Garrison, ?] [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Ulman, ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Juravinski. ?]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, survivors.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Lanski. ?] Some of them [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Erlich. ?] Some of them [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Hermann. ?] Some of them brought some furniture.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Some brought some food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Some brought some-- you know, [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Juravinski ?] put, under the pillow of my son, a $50 bill.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Before my daughter got-- was born, they made a shower.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the money-- I-- for the money, I could afford to buy a used car, my first used car here.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So if I am speaking about survivors, individual families, individual Jews in Atlanta, they helped us tremendously.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
